(angles and side lengths in triangles using ratios such as sine, cosine, and tangent.) Tj
T*
(- Core Focus: The main idea the learner must understand in this lesson: right-triangle) Tj
T*
(ratios and deciding which trig ratio fits a question.) Tj
T*
(- Application: The point where the explanation is used in practice, such as finding the) Tj
T*
(height of a building using angle of elevation.) Tj
T*
(- Common Error: A repeated learner difficulty in this topic, for example choosing the) Tj
